---
title: Swedish-Style Meatballs 2x the delicious portions!
description: This family-friendly meal built for a crowd is also speedy to make! In a quick 35 minutes you’ll serve meatballs simmered in a creamy homemade gravy over fluffy mashed potatoes. On the side is a spinach salad tossed in honey-Dijon dressing and sprinkled with nutty almonds. Serve to the extended crew, or just the regulars (with leftovers for days!).

*This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66e875f72d58b223b75b9a80-d7dd0f97.jpeg
